### Health Check
GET {{OrderManagement.API_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Detailed Health Check
GET {{OrderManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/health/detailed
Accept: application/json

### Version Info
GET {{OrderManagement.API_HostAddress}}/api/health/version
Accept: application/json

